* REQUIREMENTS

The `haskell-keepalived` packages requires following packages:
  - Parsec >= 3
  - QuickCheck
  - FileManip

All of these are available from Hackage (http://hackage.haskell.org/).

* INSTALLATION
You can configure, build, and install all inthe usual way with Cabal.

  runhaskell Setup.hs configure
  runhaskell Setup.hs build
  runhaskell Setup.hs install

* USAGE
  kc (v|verify)    [FILES...]  # Verify /etc/keepalived/keepalived.conf or
                               # specified files.

  kc (v|verify) -v [FILES...]  # Verify files and dump parsed results.

  kc (d|dump)      [FILES...]  # Parse files and dump parsed results.
